Step Inputs\: "max" - The maximum number that can be returned. "min" - The minimum number that can be returned. Step Results\: A random number between "max" and "min" (inclusive) is generated and assigned to the "randomNumber" flow variable which is defined on the Results tab . Step Responses\: "success" - The step was able to generate a random number. The flow transitions to the end step of the lane. "failure" - The step was unable to generate a random number.
